258
00:14:16,730 --> 00:14:19,358
{\an8}<i>Hopefully getting</i>
<i>his confidence rolling as well.</i>

259
00:14:19,441 --> 00:14:22,027
<i>Coca-Cola's back on.</i>
<i>Polito, lofted shot.</i>

