301
00:16:32,157 --> 00:16:34,868
Uh, what is this like
for you guys as a family?

302
00:16:34,952 --> 00:16:36,495
 Good.

303
00:16:36,578 --> 00:16:39,623
It's difficult, always,
to play finals against Dad,

304
00:16:39,707 --> 00:16:43,544
but I hope he wins today.
It would be very nice.

305
00:16:53,095 --> 00:16:56,849
The game ending
like this was also a little sad.

306
00:16:57,433 --> 00:16:59,727
The whole season, it's been hard.

307
00:16:59,810 --> 00:17:02,479
Keko, when he doesn't win,

308
00:17:02,563 --> 00:17:06,817
it doesn't always show how much
effort and work is being put into

309
00:17:07,317 --> 00:17:09,737
what's actually happening out there.

310
00:17:11,196 --> 00:17:13,323
When you get
a great opportunity like that

