00:21:27,577 --> 00:21:29,955
Both these teams are very hard to beat.

381
00:21:32,416 --> 00:21:34,710
To get to be in a semifinal

382
00:21:35,752 --> 00:21:37,504
for us was really a big deal.

383
00:21:38,630 --> 00:21:43,593
But when Bob was in the hospital,
you know, I was just thinking about him.

384
00:21:44,094 --> 00:21:48,015
We pray for him
and I hope, uh, he wakes up soon.

385
00:21:48,724 --> 00:21:50,058
Um, we're waiting for him.

386
00:21:52,853 --> 00:21:57,190
Many of my dreams in my polo career,
they came true.

387
00:21:57,983 --> 00:22:00,736
But if I win in the semifinals,

388
00:22:01,236 --> 00:22:04,614
I will play in a final
on a stage of the U.S. Open

389
00:22:05,282 --> 00:22:06,366
against my son.

390
00:22:08,869 --> 00:22:11,538
I never even dreamed about it.

391
00:22:12,497 --> 00:22:14,207
<i>Semifinal number two.</i>

392
00:22:14,291 --> 00:22:17,836
<i>Pilot in white jerseys,</i>
<i>Valiente in their blues.</i>

393
00:22:17,919 --> 00:22:22,007
<i>Going head-to-head here</i>
<i>to see who will face La Dolfina.</i>

394
00:22:22,090 --> 00:22:25,010
<i>Here comes Facundo,</i>
<i>and then Adolfo jumps back on it.</i>

395
00:22:25,093 --> 00:22:27,763
<i>We're gonna see a lot of action</i>
<i>between those two today.</i>

396
00:22:28,638 --> 00:22:31,975
<i>Oh, it's left behind. Gonna be picked up</i>
<i>by Heguy. Can he sneak it inside?</i>

397
00:22:32,059 --> 00:22:34,686
<i>Can he make him pay? Antonio Heguy!</i>

