00:22:44,738 --> 00:22:47,991
<i>Nice moves</i>
<i>on the back line there from Valiente.</i>

403
00:22:48,075 --> 00:22:49,701
{\an8}<i>And we're even here at one.</i>

404
00:22:49,785 --> 00:22:52,829
<i>Adolfo Cambiaso leads</i>
<i>the horse race out in front here.</i>

405
00:22:52,913 --> 00:22:55,916
{\an8}<i>Valiente in the lead over Pilot.</i>

406
00:22:55,999 --> 00:22:57,626
{\an8}<i>- Well done.</i>
 <i>Can he get it done?</i>

407
00:22:57,709 --> 00:22:59,836
{\an8}<i>Gonzalez! Right on through.</i>

408
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:00,921
{\an8}<i>Adolfo Cambiaso.</i>

409
00:23:01,004 --> 00:23:03,548
<i>Adolfo, not easy to do.</i>
<i>Peke Gonzalez out in front.</i>

410
00:23:03,632 --> 00:23:05,300
<i>He wants the pass. He gets the pass.</i>

411
00:23:05,384 --> 00:23:09,429
{\an8}<i>Peke Gonzalez on final approach.</i>
<i>Peke Gonzalez!</i>

412
00:23:10,472 --> 00:23:14,643
{\an8}<i>Valiente. These guys looking</i>
<i>to secure their spot in the finals.</i>

413
00:23:14,726 --> 00:23:18,146
Either I cut through
or you throw long, at the neck.

414
00:23:18,230 --> 00:23:20,607
- It was great.
- But the play was good.

415
00:23:22,901 --> 00:23:24,444
Curtis.

416
00:23:25,070 --> 00:23:27,614
- We have to change everything.
- Okay.

417
00:23:27,697 --> 00:23:30,409
I mean, it feels like
we have no play right now.

418
00:23:30,492 --> 00:23:31,326
Okay.

419
00:23:31,410 --> 00:23:35,414
Pass to me and see
if I can score a goal later.

420
00:23:36,081 --> 00:23:39,084
<i>Plenty of time.</i>
<i>Pilot needs to get to work.</i>

421
00:23:39,668 --> 00:23:41,628
<i>Adolfo brings</i>
<i>the ball into play.</i>

422
00:23:44,756 --> 00:23:47,717
<i>Paco gonna get caught</i>
<i>here on a right-of-way.</i>

423
00:23:47,801 --> 00:23:51,263
<i>It's gonna be a penalty going in favor</i>
<i>of Pilot. They needed it.</i>

424
00:23:51,346 --> 00:23:53,640
<i>Plenty of time left to go here.</i>
<i>If they can score here…</i>

425
00:23:54,266 --> 00:23:56,017
<i>Facundo on the line.</i>

426
00:23:59,646 --> 00:24:01,189
<i>And he missed it.</i>

427
00:24:01,273 --> 00:24:04,526
<i>- </i><i>Oh my goodness.</i>
<i>- </i><i>Wow. You won't see that often.</i>

428
00:24:04,609 --> 00:24:06,570
<i>On any given day, Facundo Pieres,</i>

429
00:24:06,653 --> 00:24:08,447
<i>he can beat anybody on the planet.</i>

430
00:24:08,530 --> 00:24:11,783
<i>But a little unlucky there</i>
<i>against Valiente.</i>

431
00:24:11,867 --> 00:24:13,702
<i>He never quits.</i>
<i>He continues to fight.</i>

432
00:24:13,785 --> 00:24:16,997
<i>Facundo Pieres starts</i>
<i>to drive inside. Hits it out in front.</i>

433
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:19,166
<i>Looking for Antonio Heguy.</i>

434
00:24:19,249 --> 00:24:22,544
<i>Heguy, 20 yards out.</i>
<i>A roller along the ground. It's in.</i>

435
00:24:22,627 --> 00:24:23,879
{\an8}

436
00:24:23,962 --> 00:24:25,338
{\an8}<i>They won't stop. I love it.</i>

437
00:24:25,422 --> 00:24:27,841
{\an8}<i>Facundo Pieres grabs control. Hits away.</i>

438
00:24:27,924 --> 00:24:30,010
<i>Antonio's on the move.</i>
<i>He's got him beat.</i>

